Happy Birthday, honey! You’re one year old today. Nothing in my life makes me prouder or happier than you. Waking up to your adorable little face and fluffy hair starts each day off with love and light. Before you arrived, me and your daddy were very nervous, but were ready for you to arrive and change our lives forever – and boy, did you! When you first were put on Mommy’s chest the moment you were born, I felt like I was born too – my purpose in life became clear. My purpose is you! You’re just starting to walk, little boy, and we can’t wait for you to see life through that view. We’re excited for every stage and milestone. We’re so grateful to have you in our lives and I feel blessed everyday I get to call you my son. Mommy loves you with all her heart and soul Andre Cash! Please continue to grow and spread your light to the world

Photos by the talented @m.franckephotography 
Thank you so much I could not be happier
